blocks.image_text: Cau be dung truoc cua hang, nhin chiec dien thoai voi anh mat khao khat.
blocks.dialogue_text: Con uoc gi con co du tien de mua chiec dien thoai trong tu kinh.

blocks.image_text: Nguoi cha dat tay len vai con, ra hieu di cung minh.
blocks.dialogue_text: Cha muon con di cung cha den mot noi truoc khi quyet dinh.

blocks.image_text: Hai cha con dung ben than cay lon co nhanh tam gui kho heo bam vao.
blocks.dialogue_text: Con thay cay tam gui kia khong, no song nho vao than cay khac.

blocks.image_text: Nguoi cha chi tay vao nhanh cay va giai thich, cau be lang nghe cham chu.
blocks.dialogue_text: Neu chi biet bam vao ben ngoai, den luc than cay yeu thi no cung heo tan.

blocks.image_text: Cau be mim cuoi nhe, ve mat binh tam va hieu ra van de.
blocks.dialogue_text: Con hieu roi, dieu quan trong la nang luc va tinh cach cua chinh minh.
